## Reactions Module - English
reactions-added = ✅ Reaction added! When someone says <b>{$keyword}</b>, I'll react with {$emoji}
reactions-removed = ✅ Reaction for <b>{$keyword}</b> removed.
reactions-not-found = ❌ No reaction found for that keyword.
reactions-none = 📭 No reactions set for this chat.
reactions-reset = ✅ All reactions have been cleared.
reactions-need-admin = ❌ You need to be an admin to use this command.
